Rating: 1
I always make a recipe exactly as written to have an accurate review. This recipe was very uneventful and way too bland. The edamame beans should be pre cooked as they were very underdone. The onion was very mushycompared to the rest. I recommend if you want to use this as a cold salad to mix the tomatoe in after it cools to avoid cooking the tomatoe as happens as this recipe is written. I ended up tossing the leftovers as none of us were enjoying them. There are much better edamame reicpes, I won't make this one again.

