We enjoyed the dish but made some of the modification suggested by other despondences. I used both basil and chives and a healthy amount, as my herb garden is bountiful right now. I also added feta, diced green pepper and chicken breast to make it a main dish. Salting to taste, a bit of cumin, and the juice of 1 lime, perks up the flavor a lot. It was very good and I will make it again for a quick summer meal that can be made ahead.

