Rating: 4
My entire family loves this one. It's so easy to make, and it's one of the few dishes that never comes out wrong. I leave out the onions and use sweet basil instead of chives, which makes for a slightly sweeter dish. Sometimes I add a bit of bufala mozzarella after I've put it on the plate, which turns it into a modified caprese salad. One of my husband's favorites!

