Absolutely Excellent! I have never had Edamame prior to this and served it as the vegetable for a wine dinner pairing it with Pinot Grigio. Everyone loved it & a vegetarian who was there said it was excellent. Only change I made was to add a 1/2 -1 tsp of dried italian herb mix. Finished mine with fresh basil and salt & pepper to taste. I made quadruple batch and will make it again for two more tastings this month, served it with parmesean crusted chicken over penne w/ butternut squash sauce.